# AfghanTours Copilot Design Blueprint

This brief was generated from the uploaded source ZIP `afghantours_final_site_v3.zip` and the companion CSV files in the conversation. Use it as the single source of truth for rebuilding the site in Astro + Tailwind while preserving content, route intent, and data relationships.

## Primary objective
- Rebuild the existing static AfghanTours website into a polished Astro + Tailwind site.
- Preserve page intent, existing written copy, current route structure, and CSV-driven data model.
- Use Tailwind for all new layout/styling work, but preserve the brand system from the original `bundle.css`.

