### Tailwind mapping recommendation
- `page` / `bg` → page background
- `surface` → cards, drawers, filters, section panels
- `text` + `muted` → heading/body hierarchy
- `blue` / `blue-2` → primary CTA + active states
- `gold` / `gold-2` → accent, eyebrow labels, emphasis, premium highlights
- `shadow` / `shadow2` → soft elevated travel-card styling
- `radius` / `radius2` → card and panel radii

